text: The 2019 Estonian Small Cup is the 10th season of the Estonian amateur football knockout tournament. The tournament began in March 2019, and the final will take place in September 2019 at the A. Le Coq Arena, Tallinn. Saue JK are the current cup holders. ==First Round (1/64)== The draw was made by Estonian Football Association on 13 March 2019. *League level of the club in the brackets. *Rahvaliiga RL (people's league) is a league organized by Estonian Football Association, but not part of the main league system. {| class="wikitable" style="border-collapse: collapse;" |- !style="text- align:right;
